sentences.english: The plants of courtyard appears to be more vigorous in hazy rain.
sentences.chinese: 院子的植物也因爲下雨的關係，越發顯得蔥翠。

sentences.english: Having or characterized by luxuriant vegetation.
sentences.chinese: 蔥翠的有或以茂盛植被爲特徵的。

sentences.english: The spires of churches are to be seen pricking up through the greenery .
sentences.chinese: 透過蔥翠的樹林可以看見那聳立著的教堂的塔尖。
